check.action:
Also check {{workspace_root_dir}}/context/ for workspace-level docs:
        - product-context.md → {{product_context}}
        - pm-context.md → {{product_context_legacy}} (fallback only)
        - brainstorming.md → {{brainstorming_context}}
        - global-context.md → {{global_context}}
        - inter-repo.md → {{inter_repo_context}}

Check {project-root}/_nakiros/ for:
        - architecture.md → {{arch_context}}
        - stack.md → {{stack_context}}
        - conventions.md → {{conventions_context}}
        - api.md → {{api_context}}
        - llms.txt → {{llms_context}}
        - qa-reviews/ → note presence and count
        - dev-notes/ → note presence and count
        - incidents/ → note presence and count
        - bugs/ → note presence and count

step.action:
Write context artifact to {{context_file}} in {{document_language}}:

      # Project Context — {{date}}

      ## Configuration
      - pm_tool: {{pm_tool or "not configured"}}
      - git_host: {{git_host or "not configured"}}
      - branch_pattern: {{branch_pattern or "not configured"}}
      - communication_language: {{communication_language}}
      - document_language: {{document_language}}

      ## Workspace Scope
      {{if is_multi_repo: list repos with name, role, localPath}}
      {{if not is_multi_repo: "Single-repo workspace"}}

      ## Git State
      - Current branch: {{current_branch}}
      - Recent commits:
      {{recent_commits}}
      - Uncommitted changes: {{git_status or "none"}}

      ## Existing Repo Documents
      {{if is_multi_repo:
        For each repo: "### {repo.name}\n{list of found docs with last modified dates}"
      }}
      {{if not is_multi_repo: list of found repo docs with last modified dates}}

      ## Existing Workspace Documents
      {{if workspace_config exists: list of product-context (or legacy pm-context), brainstorming, global-context, inter-repo with last modified dates}}
      {{if workspace_config does not exist: "No global workspace context configured"}}

      ## Ticket Context
      {{ticket_context if present, else "No ticket provided"}}

Display a concise summary to the user:
      - Workspace: {{single or workspace-backed with repo count}}
      - Branch: {{current_branch}}
      - Repo docs per repo: {{list grouped by repo, with freshness}}
      - Workspace docs: {{product-context or legacy pm-context, brainstorming, global-context, inter-repo if present}}
      - Ticket: {{ticketId or "none"}}
      - Artifact: {{context_file}}
